snippet.title: Character Tales - "Childe: Sigil of Permission" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
In the eyes of the Fatui Agent Javert, the Eleven Harbingers have always been figures of lofty status. Javert only remembers one time he was admonished by Sandrone, back when he was just a new recruit.
But today, Javert has suddenly been sought out by Childe with orders to accompany him to collect a certain debt. Javert is caught off guard, not sure what to expect...
